* Fred Titmus, My Life in Cricket, Blake Publishing, 2005
* Brown, Geoff and Hogsbjerg, Christian. &quot;Apartheid is not a Game: Remembering the Stop the Seventy Tour campaign.&quot; London: Redwords, 2020. .

